title: Auto Enter Nix Shells From Emacs Using Direnv
tags: @zettel _method direnv nix emacs
roam-id: 894ba3ce-2318-4f12-9591-6a6dfc1d90fb
type: text/markdown

- under your project create a `shell.nix` file
- see [[Create a Nix Shell]] for example
- under the same directory create a file called `.envrc`
- install `direnv` on your system
- install direnv package in emacs
